{"tid":619543,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"6大球星互換！曼聯同皇馬密謀驚天交易","createTime":"2018-04-06T17:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T12:32:13.000Z","uid":5006,"like":10,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"63e724facea0f8ae83ce2471377c5bcbbbae9aa8","tid":619543,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/013403_b2515240a898c793921dd2344d0e3acf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F013403_b2515240a898c793921dd2344d0e3acf.png&h=e9a7a27e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/013404_5f03d382abe48e45cf2e23a672a83484.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F013404_5f03d382abe48e45cf2e23a672a83484.png&h=b5db5ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國《曼徹斯特晚報》爆料，曼聯同皇家馬德里密謀進行驚天交易，當中牽涉到兩隊6大球星，包括紅魔嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">保羅普巴、安東尼馬迪爾同迪基亞</span>，皇馬嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">加里夫巴利、莫迪歷同卻奧斯</span>。<br />\n<br />\n或者大家會覺得，假如單純3個換3個，睇落曼聯比較蝕底，但報道提到，其實曼聯領隊莫連奴真係同保羅普巴好唔妥，同時皇馬又好想清洗加里夫巴利，只要交易籌碼傾得掂，即使最後未必會6大球星全部互換，都有可能會出現巨星轉會，大家等睇好戲啦！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180406/mobile/bkn-20180406090311058-0406_00882_001.html?eventPath=hk_sport&amp;eventID=402881074762b02a0147679f96c4415d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180406%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180406090311058-0406_00882_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dhk_sport%26eventID%3D402881074762b02a0147679f96c4415d&d=e9JVnQrpDxgtJAA6IbMN9JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=fcc740a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180406/mobile/bkn-20180406090311058-0406_00882_001.html?eventPath=hk_sport&amp;eventID=402881074762b02a0147679f96c4415d</a><br />\n<br />\n唔計身價計表現，皇馬無左摩迪同卻老，好似傷過曼聯無左普巴同迪基亞？"},{"pid":"6282a4c8412997cb5c1b8b6886c149087f01adbc","tid":619543,"uid":18430